OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy low
OL,6,Fcloud will return into the evening,
OL,7,Fwith areas of mist and fog developing
OL,8,Flater in the night. Chilly, with an
OL,9,Fisolated frost probable as winds fall
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FEarly low cloud, mist and
OL,13,Ffog soon clearing to give another fine
OL,14,Fand dry day with long sunny spells and
OL,15,Flight winds. Mild inland, but cooler
OL,16,Ftowards the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
