OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Ffine and warm during this period with
OL,7,Fplenty of sunny spells and light
OL,8,Fwinds. Chilly at times overnight with
OL,9,Fsome patchy overnight fog possible.
